# lore_orc_npc_token [9002]
#
You discover a rough golden idol, crudely fashioned.  Upon grasping
hold it it, you sense the presence of several bands of orcs nearby.
You find these units will respond to your mental control, and you
can issue the following commands to your orc units:

    ATTACK, BANNER, CONTACT, EXECUTE, GIVE, MOVE, NAME, PILLAGE,
    PROMOTE, RAZE, SEEK, STACK, TAKE, TERRORIZE, UNSTACK, WAIT
